In Articles 6 (2) and 24 (1), of Regulation (EEC) No 685/69:    - "15 750 units of account" under (a) is hereby replaced by "16 790 units of account";
- "0 729 unit of account" under (b) is hereby replaced by "0 731 unit of account";
- "9 750 %" under (c) is hereby replaced by "8 750 %".
